Heat the oil in a wok, add the onion and stir fry for three minutes.Add the mushrooms, garlic, lemongrass and Sichuan pepper. Stir fry for two minutes.Add the prawns and stir fry until just turning pink.Add the halved tomatoes, bamboo shoots, lime juice, finger lime seeds (if using) and chives. Stir fry for one minute. Spoon into a bowl and serve.